quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  36,33,"Ne eshimanyisio khubo-liloba [eliuma] liafwa khulilamusinjia mana khuchesemwo imele yabaliitsanga"
  36,34,Ne nikhukasiamwo emikunda chie tsitende nende tsizabibu ne nikhukasiamwo tsisebele
  36,35,"Kho balie khubiamo bie nende ake emikhono chiabu chilakholele tawe, koo shibakhupanga orio tawe"
  36,36,"Oluyali nilwa Nyasaye waloonga eshisatsa\tneshikhasi\tbioosi khubimelanga mwiloba nende enywe abeene nende ebiabalamanyile tawe"
  36,37,"Ne eshilo neshimanyisio shindi khubo, olwa khurusinjiamwo eshiteere nabo baba mushiilima"
  36,38,Ne eliuba lichendanga khushichelo shalio esho nisho eshichelo shia Nyasaye Owamaani Omumanyi muno
  36,39,Ne Omwesi khwakukasilia ebichelo okhula okhukalukha shingala kwali shinga likhamari liumile
  36,40,Eliuba shiniliula khumwesi nohomba eshilo okhubura eshitere nabo biosi bibotokhananga khutsinjila tsiabio
  36,41,Ne ni eshimanyisio khubo mbu efwe khwachinga olwibulo lwabu musafina yetsula
  36,42,Ne nikhwabalonjela okhurula khwifwani eyo ebiabarakanga
  36,43,Ne nikhwenya nikhubayibisia ne abulaho ubakhoonya nohomba shibahabinwa tawe
  36,44,Halali tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khwifwe nende omwikhoyo kwebise bititi
  36,45,Ne nibaboolelwa mbu; “mwilinde nende khukali imbeli wenyu nende kali inyuma wenyu mwakhaba murio mwanyoola okhubeelwa tsimbabaasi.”
  36,46,Ne ishimanyisio shiosi shiosi shia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi nishiboolela shibabukulangamwo oluchendo tawe
  36,47,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu; “rusie khubilia bia Nyasaye wenyu abakabile ,abakhayi baboolelenga Abasuubili mbu; ‘‘koo khubalisie biala ba Nyasaye niyenya nabalisia? toto enywe muli mubukori bwabulafu.”"
  36,48,Ne baboolanga mbu; “kamukhulakanga kano kalirulila lina nimuli toto abahabwene.”
  36,49,Shibalindanga halali oluyoka lulala butwsa lulibabukula nabo nibali mukhusolana
  36,50,Mana shibalinyoola okhulaamila nohomba shibalikalukha khubandu babu tawe